arrayOf("mukkar / mukkad","मक्कड़","मक्कड़ गोत्र कोटपुतली राजस्थान में है, वहां के ये 5 गांव मक्कड़ गोत्र गुर्जर हैं ","Ravi mukkar gurjar"),
arrayOf("Kandhil / Kandil","काँधिल / कांदिल","There is village like Kharaua, Bilheti and other which consist of Kandhil gotra Gurjar.\nThere is also a temple of 'Maa Shitla Kharaua' which is also related to Kandhils gurjar of Kharaua.","Ankit Singh Kandil")
